OL,3,CIronworker jailed 18 years after
OL,4,Cattack which killed boss
OL,6,FAn ironworker who attacked his boss
OL,7,Fafter he was fired, leaving him with
OL,8,Finjuries which killed him more than a
OL,9,Fdecade later, has been jailed for 12
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FOn 20 November 2006, just days after
OL,13,Flosing his job as a steel erector,
OL,14,FArjan Balla, 41, assaulted his former
OL,15,Fboss, Anastassios Delis, on Queensway
OL,16,Fin Southampton.
OL,18,FMr Delis was left unconscious after
OL,19,Fbeing punched a number of times,
OL,20,Fcausing him to fall to the ground and
OL,21,Fhit his head.
