OL,6,FIn 2007, Balla was charged with
OL,7,FSection 20 grievous bodily harm and
OL,8,Fsentenced to three years in prison.
OL,10,FAround 10 years later, on 12 December
OL,11,F2017, aged 68, Mr Delis died from his
OL,12,Finjuries having never regained
OL,13,Fconsciousness following the attack.
OL,15,FAn examination by pathologists
OL,16,Frevealed that his death was the direct
OL,17,Fresult of the injuries he sustained in
OL,18,F2006.
