OL,6,FThe Attorney General's office gave
OL,7,Fpermission in 2019 to charge Balla
OL,8,Fwith manslaughter.
OL,10,FHe was found to be using the name
OL,11,FTahir Karaj in Albania, having been
OL,12,Fdeported there following his initial
OL,13,Fsentence.
OL,15,FOnce his true identity was known,
OL,16,Fpolice received intelligence that
OL,17,FBalla was due to fly into the UK on 26
OL,18,FJanuary 2024 at Stansted Airport,
OL,19,Fwhere officers arrested him.
