OL,6,FHe was then charged with manslaughter.
OL,7,FHis fingerprints and DNA were found to
OL,8,Fmatch that of the man previously
OL,9,Fconvicted of GBH.
OL,11,FBalla was charged with manslaughter
OL,12,Fand pleaded guilty to the offence.
OL,14,FArjan Balla, of Godstone Road in
OL,15,FWhyteleafe, Surrey, appeared at
OL,16,FSouthampton Crown Court on Monday (10
OL,17,FJune) where he was jailed for his
OL,18,Finvolvement in the death of
OL,19,FAnastassios Delis from London.
