OL,6,FPolice Staff Investigator Gary Sumner
OL,7,Fsaid: "The circumstances of this case
OL,8,Fare highly unusual and extremely sad.
OL,10,F"We are thankful that the family and
OL,11,Floved ones of Anastassios Delis now
OL,12,Fhave justice, seven years after his
OL,13,Fdeath and 18 years after his assault.
